The paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The use of ensembles of pre-trained models and the approximation of the real environment using a linear combination of these models suggest that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
